# Crust Bus!!

![](https://i.imgur.com/NXIYREm.jpg)


- *mutual aid!*
- *fully mobile!*
- *free(free like the free box at a punk house) network!*
- *write and post articles!* 
- *share free technology built from the waste streams of consumer society!*
- *promote your own projects, goods or services and let the Bus spread them!*
- *wifi communism!*

Current Location: heading West on I-70 from the East Coast

